I would like to modify the flame1 demo, but I am still having trouble 
getting the original to work.  When I run it, the following error 
comes up:

Procedure: setTransport
Error:   unknown transport model.

Error in ==> @Domain1D\private\domain_methods at 12
  v = ctmethods(90, n, job, a, b, c, d); 

Error in ==> Domain1D.Domain1D at 12
      d.dom_id = domain_methods(0, 1, thermo_hndl(b), kinetics_hndl
(b), ...

Error in ==> AxisymmetricFlow at 6
m = Domain1D(1, gas);

Error in ==> flame1 at 49
f = AxisymmetricFlow(gas,'flow');

If I understand the error message, there is a problem with using the 
transport model "flow".  Does anyone know how to modify the flame1
demo so that it works properly?
